                          BUG 1                         
<--------------------------------------------------------->
Description:
    the status bar alway blinks when I move the player.
    And also at the top of the screen another status bar appears and blinks.
Solution:
    That's because the start address of upper screen and bottom screen are the same at 0x000.
    I moved the start address of upper screen to 0+18*320/4, to reserve a place for status bar.

